commitment and passion 
colleague michael woo said i feel we are being a beacon for 
the rest of the country 
mayor tom bradley urged cities nationwide to follow the lead 
councilman ernani bernardi was the lone dissenter he said the 
only way to battle the aids epidemic is to identify those with the 
disease 
