present 75 deductible which beneficiaries must pay before medicare 
starts paying for doctor bills senate 150 each year 
social security both would require all state and local 
government workers who are not covered by a public retirement plan 
to pay social security taxes 
energy initiatives the senate bill earmarks 35 billion worth 
of incentives for increasing us oil and gas exploration and 
