this is the spiritual heir to the dating game where a 
bachelor or bachelorette would ask vaguely suggestive questions 
to a trio of hidden singles bachelor no 1 if you were a main 
dish what would you be 
love connection singles audit three videos select a 
partner go out on a date and agree not to discuss the date until 
